Camilla Belle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Camilla_Belle 0 Camilla Belle Routh (born October 2, 1986) is a Brazilian-American actress, director, writer and producer. Her works include The Ballad of Jack and Rose, When a Stranger Calls, 10,000 BC, and Push.
